            <title>[LU-10072] Error on Mount OST</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10072</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Error on mounting OST. Can you please help on this.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;root@10-64-13-39 xxx-user&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;# mount -t lustre /dev/xvdx /mnt/ost0&lt;br/&gt;
mount.lustre: mount /dev/xvdk at /mnt/ost0 failed: No such file or directory&lt;br/&gt;
Is the MGS specification correct?&lt;br/&gt;
Is the filesystem name correct?&lt;br/&gt;
If upgrading, is the copied client log valid? (see upgrade docs)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;dmesg&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
LDISKFS-fs (xvdk): mounted filesystem with ordered data mode. quota=on. Opts:&lt;br/&gt;
SELinux: initialized (dev xvdk, type ldiskfs), not configured for labeling&lt;br/&gt;
Lustre: 3981:0:(client.c:2063:ptlrpc_expire_one_request()) @@@ Request sent has timed out for sent delay: &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;sent 1507129204/real 0&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;  req@ffff88009f123c80 x1580338739413020/t0(0) o250-&amp;gt;MGC10.64.5.131@tcp@10.64.5.131@tcp:26/25 lens 520/544 e 0 to 1 dl 1507129209 ref 2 fl Rpc:XN/0/ffffffff rc 0/-1&lt;br/&gt;
LustreError: 13a-8: Failed to get MGS log temp-OST0000 and no local copy.&lt;br/&gt;
LustreError: 15c-8: MGC10.64.5.131@tcp: The configuration from log &apos;temp-OST0000&apos; failed (-2). This may be the result of communication errors between this node and the MGS, a bad configuration, or other errors. See the syslog for more information.&lt;br/&gt;
LustreError: 5651:0:(obd_mount_server.c:1309:server_start_targets()) failed to start server temp-OST0000: -2&lt;br/&gt;
LustreError: 5651:0:(obd_mount_server.c:1798:server_fill_super()) Unable to start targets: -2&lt;br/&gt;
LustreError: 5651:0:(obd_mount_server.c:1512:server_put_super()) no obd temp-OST0000&lt;br/&gt;
Lustre: server umount temp-OST0000 complete&lt;br/&gt;
LustreError: 5651:0:(obd_mount.c:1426:lustre_fill_super()) Unable to mount  (-2)&lt;/p&gt;

